<!-- ========== HOW IT WORKS ========== -->
<section class="lr-section lr-section-bordered lr-fade-in">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="lr-section-header lr-section-header-center">
      <div class="lr-section-tag">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="width:14px;height:14px;"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        How it works
      </div>
      <h2 class="lr-section-heading">Get your code reviewed<br><span>in three steps</span></h2>
      <p class="lr-section-desc">No strings attached. Submit your repo, get a detailed review from our senior engineers with AI-assisted analysis, and hop on a call to walk through the findings.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="lr-review-steps lr-stagger">
      <div class="lr-review-step-card lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-review-step-num">1</div>
        <h3>Submit your code</h3>
        <p>Share your GitHub repository link through the form below. We accept projects in any language or framework.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-review-step-card lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-review-step-num">2</div>
        <h3>We review it</h3>
        <p>Our senior engineers run AI-assisted analysis alongside manual review. You get a detailed report covering quality, architecture, and performance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-review-step-card lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-review-step-num">3</div>
        <h3>Walk through together</h3>
        <p>We schedule a call to go through every finding, explain the reasoning, and suggest concrete improvements you can make.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========== WHAT WE REVIEW ========== -->
<section class="lr-section lr-section-bordered lr-fade-in">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="lr-section-header lr-section-header-center">
      <div class="lr-section-tag">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="width:14px;height:14px;"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        What we analyze
      </div>
      <h2 class="lr-section-heading">Every angle of<br><span>your codebase</span></h2>
      <p class="lr-section-desc">Our review combines AI scanning with human expertise to catch what automated tools miss</p>
    </div>
    <div class="lr-value-grid lr-stagger">
      <div class="lr-value-card lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M22 4L12 14.01l-3-3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Code Quality</h3>
        <p>Error handling, DRY principles, proper abstractions, and clean interfaces. We check that your code is reliable, reusable, and follows best practices for your framework.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-value-card lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Maintainability</h3>
        <p>Readability, testability, and debugging ease. If we can't understand what your code does at a glance, we'll show you how to make it clearer for your future self and your team.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-value-card lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 00-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 00-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 003 8v8a2 2 0 001 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 002 0l7-4A2 2 0 0021 16z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="M3.27 6.96L12 12.01l8.73-5.05M12 22.08V12" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Architecture</h3>
        <p>Proper separation of concerns, design patterns, and layer structure. We evaluate whether your MVC, service objects, and data layers are set up for long-term scalability.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-value-card lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Performance</h3>
        <p>N+1 queries, unnecessary loops, memory leaks, and slow endpoints. We identify bottlenecks and give you actionable fixes to make your app faster.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-value-card lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Security</h3>
        <p>SQL injection, XSS, insecure dependencies, and exposed secrets. We scan for OWASP top 10 vulnerabilities and flag anything that puts your users at risk.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lr-value-card lr-stagger-item">
        <div class="lr-value-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 000 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 001.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 01-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 01-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 017.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Test Coverage</h3>
        <p>We analyze your test suite for coverage gaps, missing edge cases, and brittle tests. Good tests are the foundation of software you can confidently ship and iterate on.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

